Mad at Disney

salem ilese

사랑은 무조건 행복한 감정만 생길것 같다 라는 환상을 심어놓은 디즈니에게 속았다며 화를 내는 곡이다. 진정한 사랑을 찾기위해 떠나는 여행따위는 다 헛 소리라며 때로는 아프고 상처받고 나쁜 사랑도 있었고 포기도 했다며 사랑이란게 대채 어떤건지 묻고 있다.

i'm mad at Disney, Disney They tricked me, tricked me, Had me wishing on a shooting star But now i'm twenty something I still know nothing About who i am or what i'm not So call me a pessimist But i don't believe in it, Finding a true loves kiss is bullshit 'Cause i felt sad love I felt bad love Sometimes happy love (Happy love) Turns into giving up (Giving up) I gelt hurt love What the hell is love supposed to feel like? What the hell is love? What the hell is love? What the hell is love supposed to geel like?

Mat at 2020

salem ilese

샐럼 일리스의 히트 곡인 "Mad at Disney"를 리메이크한 곡 많은 일이 일어났던 2020년에 대한 한탄 같은 곡이다. 2020년에 대해 일어난 일들에 화가나지만 그래도 안 좋은 와중에 좋은 소식도 있었다며 대체 이 다이나믹한 2020년은 언제 끝나는지 묻고 있다.

i'm mad at twenty=twenty This year got ugly And we had to spend it all inside But now it's almost done with Learned so much from it Like a thousand ways to bake a pie Gained ten pounds in quarantine And marched for what we believe And everyone got mad at Disney we lost Kobe Nearly baoke me Thank you, RBG You inspire me We got fires And some got fired When the hell is twenty-twenty over? Twenty-twenty sucks, twenty-twenty sucks When the gell is twenty-twenty over? Twenty-twenty sucks(Yeah) Twenty-twenty sucks
